{
  "stem": "2353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- at that time, I was working in a doctor's office as a physiotherapist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was tight, but we managed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I joined the Park Central AA, which wasn't a big deal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I competed in 1937 in the American championships in high jump and shot put.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I weighed about 112 pounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you ever seen shot putters, they're like this, you know, really big.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I won.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was one woman from Tuskegee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She thought she had won because I-- I did high jump at the same time, and I  had to come back and do my shot put afterwards.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came, this nothing, skinny, 112 pound person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- I threw the thing once.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had won.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it-- it was hysterical, because they took pictures of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I must've been half the size of this woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a funny thing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Friends of ours in South-- South Africa went to the movies one night, and in the news reel, there was I and this woman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They showed-- showed us together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they thought it was just the funniest sight ever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I have tried to find the picture, but I never could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the following year, I competed again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I won again the-- in high jump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the following year, I was just getting ready in the morning to-- yeah, it's the same morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- I just packed my gear to go to another championship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And word came over the radio that the war had started in Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I said, there are more important things in this world than high jumping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I quit right then and there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
